- REST is am architechtural style that defines a set of constraints(some defined rules) to be used for creating web services

- CRUD operations(DB er) handle korte REST APIs use kora hoy

-CRUD(Create,Read,Update,Delete)

- Check Twitter API

--Blog(https://stackoverflow.blog/2020/03/02/best-practices-for-rest-api-design/) -For better understanding

-Use nouns instead of verbs in endpoint paths

-----CRUD Operation----
-GET (retrieving resources)
-POST(submitting new data to server)
-PUT (to update existing data)
-PATCH (to update existing data partially)
-DELETE (to remove data)

-Resources refers to something on which we are gonna perform CRUD operation

